com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models

Class ListMessagesOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.QueueServiceOptions
      • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.ListMessagesOptions

  • public class ListMessagesOptions
extends QueueServiceOptions
    Represents the options that may be set on a listMessages request. These options include a server response timeout for the request, the number of messages to retrieve from the queue, and the visibility timeout to set on the retrieved messages.
